ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisAppointment of PATRICIA ANNE KENNEDY of Delta, British Columbia, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of William S. Deluce.
